# Instructions
## Add dotfile to be tracked
```
config add ~/vimrc
config commit -s -m "add ~/.vimrc"
config push
```
## Modify dotfile
```
config add ~/.vimrc
config commit
config push
```
## View modified dotfiles
```
config status
```
## View tracked dotfiles
```
config ls-tree master --name-only
```

# Reference
* https://www.atlassian.com/git/tutorials/dotfiles
